Author: GymForVitalik
Title: 🔥 [ANN][ICO] FitVitalik - Our Hero Needs Help 🔥
Body: Because some people are much too busy thinking about our future. They’ve forgotten to think about theirs.    Contribution address: 0x8ef24a1f5053b885d81044a3173e38bbf24f7371    What Is FitVitalik ICO?  FitVitalik is the first useful ICO that is intended to help the one and only Vitalik BTCuterin get better health and become a fitter person. It is a shame that this guy is making history and is not able to take proper care of himself. A lot of people are concerned about Vitalik's health and this ICO will change his future. We need more cool stuff from Vitalik, we need healthy Ethereum and we need healthy leader that will create more products and will finally make Ethereum get to the moon.   Roadmap  Phase 1 Q4 2017: - ICO start - Token listing on several exchanges - Vitalik is informed about the great plan - Crypto community contibutes to motivate Vitalik hit the gym  Phase 02 Q1 2018 - Vitalik choses his dream-gym - The first goal of his choice is set  Phase 03 Q2 2018 - Vitalik achieves the first goal  Phase 04 Q3 2018 - Vitalik continues doing sports and motivates other people to do so   Key Features  ICO START DATE 2017-11-25 NO PRESALE NO SALE BONUSES ALL 100% OF TOKENS ARE FOR SALE ONLY 14 DAYS SALE PERIOD HARD CAP 2000 ETH THE TOKENS ARE AVAILABLE RIGHT AFTER ICO COMPLETION FOR MORE INFO VISIT HTTPS://FITVITALIK.IO CONTACT: INFO@FITVITALIK.IO
